column5: It will be great to get back to this lake,after two yrs. of not being able to go. the lake in the last two yrs very little pressure.should be some big girls to be caught
Try to leave a few for those of us that are arriving after you

Ron. are you flying in from St Anne Du Lac. Certainly a much better road trip. My Honda Pilot has never recovered from the three trips to Clova. I hope this recent Covid variant doesn't tighten up the border again. Can't beat the fishing up there, have a great trip. Ron
